{"tid":913271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"娥特閂埋門　同美商會密密斟","createTime":"2018-11-23T09:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T12:04:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6ffe18b606ea3aa38b4152d126a90b11d2589154","tid":913271,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181123/large/a2003a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181123%2Flarge%2Fa2003a.jpg&h=ea69e295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前排美國國會先出咗份報告，建議檢視吓美國對香港嘅軍用、民用技術出口管制政策，嚇到自由黨急急腳抽起有關《基本法》23條立法嘅議案，不過「好打得」嘅特首林鄭月娥（圖）仲好口硬，話人哋份報告指控失實、雙重標準同埋係戴咗有色眼鏡。過咗冇幾耐箒，原來林鄭又靜雞雞去咗同香港美國商會食飯。<br />\n<br />\n話說噚日香港美國商會有個感恩節午餐會，盛傳林鄭都去，於是八方就去八吓啦。點知去到先發現，根本林鄭冇去到，只係有幾位問責局長，例如創科局長楊偉雄、財庫局長劉怡翔等現身。<br />\n<br />\n但係八方依然死心不息，無理由無啦啦傳出林鄭出席美國商會午宴嘅，於是問吓特首辦。點知特首辦確認，林鄭前日已出席美國商會嘅感恩節午膳，所以噚日冇再現身。咁到底林鄭閉門同美國商會講啲乜？特首辦就話由於係閉門活動，唔可以透露談話內容喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181123/20552708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F20552708&d=1hC2mXRqFVwtGDzsKQdeR3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c9b6923e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F20552708&h=54764e37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181123/20552708</a>"},{"pid":"7b8ecb59bf5486d6a119d8c75d25383e6fbf9bc8","tid":913271,"uid":158613,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:27:51.000Z","msg":"M腿救港"},{"pid":"8228a2eb57373b338827b1e32a9f712e1070d604","tid":913271,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c49177001e64a713808536c646013d9fd4ac146","t